description: LibriVox recording of Ontario Public School Geography by (the) Ontario Dept. of Education. This Ontario Public School textbook, published in 1922, contains some fascinating facts of a world which no longer exists. It seems, by modern day standards, politically-incorrect in some of the descriptions of people and places. (Summary by David Lawrence) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B Format Available
